A customer reported that the Atlassian LDAP interface doesn't use the ["derefAliases" setting|http://java.sun.com/products/jndi/tutorial/ldap/misc/aliases.html]. 

This means that the value will be switched to the default value, which is {{always}}, causing a bad performance in big LDAP instance.

Preferably an ability to enable/disable this functionality in the {{atlassian-user.xml}} config file is available.

